#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Updates stock and currency prices from online sources using the <link "
"linkend=\"details.investments.onlinequotes\">Online Price Quotes</link> "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"Posodablja cene delnic in valut iz spletnih virov s funkcijo <link linkend="
"\"details.investments.onlinequotes\">Spletne kotacije cen</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:776
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Consistency Check</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preverjanje doslednosti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Runs a check on your file, fixes any problems it can, and displays a report "
"of the results."
msgstr ""
"Zažene preverjanje vaše datoteke, odpravi morebitne težave ,kolikor jih "
"lahko, in prikaže poročilo o rezultatih."

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make a backup of your file before running this option."
msgstr "Preden zaženete to možnost, naredite varnostno kopijo datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Performance-Test</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preizkus uspešnosti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid "Runs a performance test on your file and displays the results."
msgstr "Zažene preizkus učinkovitosti vaše datoteke in prikaže rezultate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Generate Database SQL</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Generiraj bazo podatkov SQL</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generates the SQL necessary to create a database."
msgstr "Generira SQL, potreben za kreiranje baze podatkov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Debug timers</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpravi napake časovnikov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:811
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a tool for developers."
msgstr "To je orodje za razvijalce."

#. Tag: title
#: reference.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings and Help Menus"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitev in Pomoči"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Settings and Help menus of &kmymoney; are based on those described in "
"<ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html\">&kde; Fundamentals</ulink> with "
"some additional items."
msgstr ""
"Menija Nastavitve in Pomoč &kmymoney; temeljijo na opisanih v <ulink url="
"\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html\">&kde; Osnove</ulink> z nekaterimi "
"dodatnimi predmeti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Enable all messages</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Omogoči vsa sporočila</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Re-enables any messages you may have turned off by checking "
"<guimenuitem>Don't tell me about this again</guimenuitem> in a dialog box."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno omogoči vsa sporočila, ki ste jih morda izklopili tako, da ste v "
"pogovornem oknu označili <guimenuitem>Ne govori mi več o tem</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Language...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj jezik...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the language used by &kmymoney; depends on the system wide "
"settings for location or locale. This allows you to change that language, "
"and to set a fallback language, which is used for text which has not been "
"translated into the primary language."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je jezik, ki ga uporablja &kmymoney; odvisen od sistemskih "
"nastavitev za lokacijo ali jezik. To vam omogoča, da spremenite ta jezik in "
"nastavite nadomestni jezik, ki se uporablja za besedilo, ki ni bilo "
"prevedeno v primarni jezik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Keyboard Shortcuts...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo>&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>,</keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice na "
"tipkovnici...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:858
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to add or modify keyboard shortcuts for various actions."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča dodajanje ali spreminjanje bližnjic na tipkovnici za različna "
"dejanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: reference.docbook:867
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Aqbanking</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj Aqbanking</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:871
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure online banking settings, but only if the KBanking module is "
"enabled. More information may be found in the section on configuring the "
"<link linkend=\"details.settings.plugins.kbanking\">KBanking plugin</link> "
"as well as in the <ulink url=\"https://www.gnucash.org/docs/v5/C/gnucash-"
"manual/tools-on-line-banking.html#tool-aqb-modules\">&gnucash; "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte nastavitve spletnega bančništva, vendar le, če je omogočen "
"modul KBanking. Več informacij lahko najdete v razdelku o konfiguraciji "
"<link linkend=\"details.settings.plugins.kbanking\">vtičnika KBanking</link> "
"kot tudi v dokumentaciji <ulink url=\"https://www.gnucash.org /docs/v5/C/"
"gnucash-manual/tools-on-line-banking.html#tool-aqb-modules\">&gnucash;</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: reference.docbook:879
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The process of setting up online access in AqBanking is described in <ulink "
"url=\"https://wiki.gnucash.org/wiki/De/Onlinebanking-Einrichtungsassistent"
"\">the &gnucash; wiki (German only)</ulink>. This menu entry brings you to "
"the dialog shown in step #3. The process until step #18 is the same for "
"KMyMoney. Once done, you can map the account in &kmymoney; using "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Map account</guisubmenu> and select "
"the account from the list provided. From there, simply use <guimenu>Account</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Update account</guisubmenu>, or in case you have more "
"than one online account mapped <guimenu>Account</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Update "
"all accounts</guisubmenu>."
msgstr ""
"Postopek vzpostavitve spletnega dostopa v AqBanking je opisan v <ulink url="
"\"https://wiki.gnucash.org/wiki/De/Onlinebanking-Einrichtungsassistent"
"\">&gnucash; wiki (samo v nemščini)</ulink>. Ta vnos v meniju vas pripelje "
"do pogovornega okna, prikazanega v 3. koraku. Postopek do koraka #18 je enak "
"za KMyMoney. Ko končate, lahko preslikate račun v &kmymoney; z uporabo "
"<guimenu>Račun</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preslikaj račun</guisubmenu> in "
"izberite račun s ponujenega seznama. Od tam preprosto uporabite "
"<guimenu>Račun</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Posodobi račun</guisubmenu> ali v "
"primeru, da imate več kot en spletni račun preslikanega <guimenu>Račun</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Posodobite vse račune</guisubmenu>."

